            <sparkle:version>50</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.16.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Audio Unit Plugin support (Beta) — load EQ, dynamics, and filter plugins into the audio chain</li>
                    <li>Plugin picker filtered to restoration-relevant AU plugins only</li>
